---
layout: base.njk
title: Careers
description: "Join our team at Meridian Osteopathy. Osteopath jobs in Christchurch, New Zealand. Structured mentorship program and career growth."
---

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero" style="background-image: url('/images/hero-careers.jpg');">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>Careers &amp; Recruitment</h1>
    <p>Apply online &bull; Speak to team</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- About working here -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="careers-content">
      <h2>Join Our Team at Meridian Osteopathy</h2>

      <p>We're not just offering a job — we're inviting you to embark on a <strong>rewarding career journey</strong> within a supportive and visionary environment.</p>

      <p>Whether you're a <strong>recent graduate</strong> or a <strong>seasoned practitioner</strong>, we welcome dedicated individuals who are passionate about making a real difference in people's lives.</p>

      <p>For acupuncturists, all applicants — whether based in New Zealand or overseas — must hold current registration with the <strong>Chinese Medicine Council of New Zealand (CMCNZ)</strong>, or be eligible to obtain it prior to commencing practice. This is a mandatory requirement and ensures the highest standard of care for our patients.</p>

      <p>At every stage, you'll benefit from <strong>continuous learning opportunities</strong>, a collaborative team environment, and the satisfaction of positively impacting our patients. Our remuneration packages are competitive and tailored to experience, and we offer <strong>relocation assistance</strong> for those moving to Christchurch. Overseas applicants are welcome — we can assist with guidance on CMCNZ registration, visa applications, and help you settle into Christchurch.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Current Vacancies -->
<section class="section section-light">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Current Vacancies</h2>

    {% if careers.vacancies and careers.vacancies.length > 0 %}

      <p class="subtitle" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">We're hiring! See our open positions below and apply using the form further down the page.</p>

      <div class="vacancy-table">
        <div class="vacancy-table-header">
          <span>Position</span>
          <span>Type</span>
          <span>Requirements</span>
          <span></span>
        </div>
        {% for v in careers.vacancies %}
        <div class="vacancy-row">
          <span class="vacancy-title">{{ v.title }}</span>
          <span class="vacancy-type vacancy-type--{{ v.type | lower | replace(' ', '-') }}">{{ v.type }}</span>
          <span class="vacancy-requirements">{{ v.requirements }}</span>
          <a href="#apply" class="btn btn-gold" style="font-size:0.82rem; padding:8px 18px; white-space:nowrap;">Apply Now</a>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

    {% else %}

      <div class="vacancy-empty">
        <div class="vacancy-empty-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="1.8" width="48" height="48">
            <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="20"/>
            <path d="M24 14v12M24 32v2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>No open positions right now</h3>
        <p>We don't have any active vacancies at the moment, but we'd still love to hear from you. If you're a passionate healthcare professional interested in joining the Meridian Osteopathy team, submit your CV below — we keep all expressions of interest on file and will reach out when a suitable opportunity arises.</p>
        <a href="#apply" class="btn btn-gold" style="margin-top: 8px;">Register Your Interest</a>
      </div>

    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Application Form -->
<section class="section" id="apply">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2>Application Form</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">Apply or register your interest to work at Meridian Osteopathy</p>

    <form name="career-application" method="POST" data-netlify="true" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="form-container" style="text-align: left; margin-top: 32px;">
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="career-application">

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Name <span class="required">*</span></label>
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Enter your name" required>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Email <span class="required">*</span></label>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Phone <span class="required">*</span></label>
        <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Enter your phone" required>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>I am a: <span class="required">*</span></label>
        <select name="applicant-type" required>
          <option value="" disabled selected>Recent Graduate / Experienced Osteopath / Other</option>
          <option value="recent-graduate">Recent Graduate</option>
          <option value="experienced-osteopath">Experienced Osteopath</option>
          <option value="cmcnz-acupuncturist">CMCNZ Registered Acupuncturist</option>
          <option value="other">Other</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Message</label>
        <textarea name="message" placeholder="Your message..."></textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="file-uploads">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>CV/Resume</label>
          <input type="file" name="cv" accept=".pdf,.doc,.docx">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Cover Letter</label>
          <input type="file" name="cover-letter" accept=".pdf,.doc,.docx">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 16px;">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold">Submit Application</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
